{"tid":1914722,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"Ampere 推出 80 核處理器向 AMD 宣戰：效能比 AMD 最強的 EPYC 7742 處理器高 1.04 倍！","createTime":"2020-03-07T17:35:10.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-12T09:25:17.000Z","uid":1886,"like":8,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":42,"replies":[{"pid":"33dbf7c2961912e28418a0a010a35293c3ada84f","tid":1914722,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-07T17:35:10.000Z","msg":"Ampere 在數據中心處理器領域正式與 AMD 及 Intel「開戰」，在近日推出了業界首個基於 Arm 架構的 80 核心 64-bit 伺服器處理器「Ampere Altra」，「Ampere Altra」採用了台積電 7nm 工藝，運行時脈為 3GHz，單路最高支援 4TB 記憶體及 128 條 PCIe 4.0 通道，Ampere 稱 Altra 的處理性能比 AMD 最強的 EPYC 7742 處理器高 1.04 倍，更是 Intel Xeon Platinum 8280 處理器的 2.23 倍。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://file1.hkepc.net/2020/03/source/05140353331736081610.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffile1.hkepc.net%2F2020%2F03%2Fsource%2F05140353331736081610.jpg&h=6628b474&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n對於 Ampere 公司可能大家都不太熟識，Ampere 其實是一間新的創企公司，成立於 2017 年 10 月，總部位於美國加利福利亞州聖克拉拉，專注於雲端運算及邊緣運算方面所用高性能微處理器的研發，致力於 Arm 架構伺服器處理器的設計，在成立初期由 Carlyle Group 凱雷投資集團提供資金支持，而在 2019 在 4 月份，甲骨文向 Ampere 投入 4000 萬美元的資金。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://file1.hkepc.net/2020/03/source/05140352321600529057.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffile1.hkepc.net%2F2020%2F03%2Fsource%2F05140352321600529057.jpg&h=bc261be8&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n至於 Ampere 的 CEO Renee James 更大有來頭，Renee James 在未加入 Ampere 公司之前，其實在 Intel 是已工作了 28 年，一路從研發工程師升到了僅次於當時的 CEO Brain Krzanich 的二把手，並最終成為了總裁，直到 2016 年才離開 Intel。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://file1.hkepc.net/2013/09/source/2719175272699241916.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffile1.hkepc.net%2F2013%2F09%2Fsource%2F2719175272699241916.jpg&h=01053b4b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\">▲ Renee James 曾在 Intel 工作了 28 年</span></div><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hkepc.com/19107/%E6%89%93%E7%88%86_AMD_64_%E6%A0%B8%E5%BF%837nm80%E6%A0%B8%E5%BF%83_AMPERE_%E5%85%A8%E6%96%B0_ALTRA_%E8%99%95%E7%90%86%E5%99%A8%E5%8D%B3%E5%B0%87%E4%B8%8A%E5%B8%82\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkepc.com%2F19107%2F%25E6%2589%2593%25E7%2588%2586_AMD_64_%25E6%25A0%25B8%25E5%25BF%25837nm80%25E6%25A0%25B8%25E5%25BF%2583_AMPERE_%25E5%2585%25A8%25E6%2596%25B0_ALTRA_%25E8%2599%2595%25E7%2590%2586%25E5%2599%25A8%25E5%258D%25B3%25E5%25B0%2587%25E4%25B8%258A%25E5%25B8%2582&d=z2r7XlCbtqTRl1EuzFzNuKjD3B6m7wr0JF9t5bmmazk%3D&h=8e9c3b80\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hkepc.com/19107/%E6%89%93%E7%88%86_AMD_64_%E6%A0%B8%E5%BF%837nm80%E6%A0%B8%E5%BF%83_AMPERE_%E5%85%A8%E6%96%B0_ALTRA_%E8%99%95%E7%90%86%E5%99%A8%E5%8D%B3%E5%B0%87%E4%B8%8A%E5%B8%82</a>"},{"pid":"4066729f4844148c5c5f6173c8a1b5982e2fd358","tid":1914722,"uid":1886,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-07T17:36:59.000Z","msg":"Renee James 在成立 Ampere 時已表明欲挑戰英特爾在伺服器晶片的霸主地位，而在近日就正式推出了業界首個基於 Arm 架構的 80 核心 64-bit 伺服器處理器「Ampere Altra」，「Ampere Altra」更全球已知核心數量最多的處理器，核心數量比 AMD 最新推出 64 核心的 EPYC 7742 處理器還要多。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://file1.hkepc.net/2020/03/source/05141101611714762767.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffile1.hkepc.net%2F2020%2F03%2Fsource%2F05141101611714762767.jpg&h=6a964925&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n「Ampere Altra」處理器基於 Arm Neoverse N1 平台，採用台積電 7nm 工藝技術獲得更高能效，晶片電路的寬度為七十億分之一米。處理器的運行時脈為 3GHz，支援 8 個 2DPC 72 位 DDR4-3200 記憶體通道，可提供單路最高 4TB 的記憶體容量，同時每路支援最高 128 條 PCIe PCIe 4.0 通道 ，功耗為 210W。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://file1.hkepc.net/2020/03/source/05135550501991662506.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffile1.hkepc.net%2F2020%2F03%2Fsource%2F05135550501991662506.jpg&h=ae48e407&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://file1.hkepc.net/2020/03/source/05135551511072857938.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffile1.hkepc.net%2F2020%2F03%2Fsource%2F05135551511072857938.jpg&h=a200e6ab&s={SIZE}\" /></div>"},{"pid":"71f40b0d5da1ab19a2bd669595a65639fac22c33","tid":1914722,"uid":1886,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-07T17:38:01.000Z","msg":"在原始性能上，Altra 處理器比 AMD 的 EPYC 7742 處理器快 1.04 倍，比 Xeon Platinum 8280 高出 2.23 倍，而在雲端工作負載處理上，Altra 在電源效率上比 EPYC 7742 高 14%，是 Intel Xeon Platinum 8280 處理器的 2.1 倍。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://file1.hkepc.net/2020/03/source/05135550501111106510.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffile1.hkepc.net%2F2020%2F03%2Fsource%2F05135550501111106510.jpg&h=e1517a31&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://file1.hkepc.net/2020/03/source/051440404086309204.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffile1.hkepc.net%2F2020%2F03%2Fsource%2F051440404086309204.jpg&h=1ca106c7&s={SIZE}\" /></div>"},{"pid":"8a9c7207b0cafcad7694ec37c56ccb645410e31d","tid":1914722,"uid":1886,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-07T17:38:52.000Z","msg":"目前在 x86 數據中心處理器領域，Intel 仍然以超過 95% 的市場份額佔據絕對主導，其餘就是 AMD，在短時間內市場格局不會有較大變動，但不可否認，Arm 架構 CPU 家族中正不斷湧現新晉挑戰者，向 Intel 數據中心處理器領域發起有力挑戰，為數據中心處理器市場注入新的活力。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://file1.hkepc.net/2020/03/source/0513555454808705813.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffile1.hkepc.net%2F2020%2F03%2Fsource%2F0513555454808705813.jpg&h=3c09891d&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\nRenee James 在接受外媒採訪時亦表示，在核心數、性能、功耗等方面 Altra 處理器已領先了對手 Intel Xeon 及 AMD EPYC 處理器，目前已經開始提供 Ampere Altra 晶片樣品，預計將於 2020 年中期全面投產。"},{"pid":"c98da6b415820419b9b17eddd339efc9c2b320be","tid":1914722,"uid":1886,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-07T17:39:27.000Z","msg":"不過僅僅「Ampere Altra」處理器是開始，Renee James 透露了一年後將在市場上推出另一種代號為 Mystique 的新產品，將會比繼續提高核心數比 Altra 的 80 個核心還要多，並確立在核心數量方面的領導地位。 <br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://file1.hkepc.net/2020/03/source/05135555551419279363.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffile1.hkepc.net%2F2020%2F03%2Fsource%2F05135555551419279363.jpg&h=da7b6303&s={SIZE}\" /></div>"},{"pid":"4785c7dadc39cd50aa9246b6614ecf9da494609b","tid":1914722,"uid":76705,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-07T17:40:19.000Z","msg":"1.04 倍<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b816c98a19fb511a58a804ad0f20c5ba3d24bfc","tid":1914722,"uid":63124,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-07T17:44:26.000Z","msg":"過幾年仲係到先再講啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be6e317657b41255a5235dbf7e77a32069a3c940","tid":1914722,"uid":153571,"like":27,"dislike":1,"score":26,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-07T17:53:18.000Z","msg":"80核先快64核1.04倍就算把啦"},{"pid":"1aa949459abde303362a3cacbb67275ec3168384","tid":1914722,"uid":89514,"like":1,"dislike":7,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-07T17:56:57.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"eaa2f61224b6a06e7a05ba33842677407b6ec8a4","tid":1914722,"uid":165773,"like":0,"dislike":8,"score":-8,"quote":{"pid":"be6e317657b41255a5235dbf7e77a32069a3c940","tid":1914722,"uid":153571,"like":27,"dislike":1,"score":26,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-07T17:53:18.000Z","msg":"80核先快64核1.04倍就算把啦"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-07T18:03:29.000Z","msg":"如果係真嘅咁其實好勁喎<br />\n64x2=128<br />\n80都未去到128已經快double"},{"pid":"91f508af4272632280319f140ea3fd1278027cd7","tid":1914722,"uid":326061,"like":0,"dislike":10,"score":-10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-07T18:06:29.000Z","msg":"AMD不了"},{"pid":"d70f6afe1f132b7ca97d322d2ece9249be199635","tid":1914722,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"91f508af4272632280319f140ea3fd1278027cd7","tid":1914722,"uid":326061,"like":0,"dislike":10,"score":-10,"